name: Winston's Sweet 16
description:
This party looks fun and Winston wants to join in!

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Help guide Winston in this 3D Runner, as he runs, jumps, and dodges his way through the party! Try your best to collect all the candle treats his owners made for him, while getting the end in the best time possible!

Controls:
Mouse - Movement
Space - Jump
R - Reset
Esc - Quit
